room_title: Escape room "Hive Mind" by Puzzah! in Denver

room_description: You are workers in a colony of bees. Your new assignment is helping the hive increase honey production. This could be a golden opportunity if you can learn the job quickly, perform well, and keep the queen happy. You need to hit the air flying!
